根据丁香医生，截至 3 月 7 日 20:52 时，全国现存确诊病例 22184 例，累计确诊病例 80814 例，现存疑似病例 502 例。
According to Dr. Lilac, as of 20: 52 on March 7, there were 22,184 confirmed cases nationwide, 80,814 confirmed cases and 502 existing suspected cases.
其中，重症病例 5489 例，死亡病例 3073 例，累计治愈病例 55557 例。
Of these, 5,489 were serious, 3,073 were fatal and 55557 were cured.
。
.
截至 3 月 7 日，除中国以外，全球现存确诊病例为 19637 例，累计确诊病例 22679 例，死亡 436 例，累计治愈 2606。
As of March 7, there were 1,9637 confirmed cases worldwide, with a cumulative total of 22,679 confirmed cases and 436 deaths, with 2,606 cases cured.
除中国外，目前全球有 92 个国家出现了新冠肺炎确诊病人。
In addition to China, 92 countries have now been diagnosed with pneumonia in the new crown.
。
