从意大利返京的新冠肺炎患者因瞒报被立案http://www.bjnews.com.cn/news/2020/03/07/700506.html据@平安北京 通报，3 月 4 日，廖某君、廖某海等两家一行 8 人从意大利乘机到北京首都国际机场，之后，其中 4 人被北京市确诊为新冠肺炎病例。
New Crown Pneumonia patients returning to Beijing from Italy were registered for underreporting http: / / www.bjnews.com.cn / news / 2020 / 03 / 07 / 700506.html @ Ping An Beijing informed that on March 4, eight people from two families, Liao and Liao, flew from Italy to Beijing's Capital International Airport.
廖某君、廖某海一家长期在意大利经商，2 月底出现发热、干咳等症状，在登机前使用药物退烧降温，在抵达时，“存在不如实填写《中华人民共和国出/入境健康申明卡》的情形，给同机人员造成传染风险。
Liao a prince, Liao a long-term business in Italy, February fever, dry cough and other symptoms, before boarding the use of drugs to cool down, upon arrival, "the People's Republic of China issued / entered the Health Declaration Card falsely filled out, posing a risk of contagion to the same crew.
”3 月 6 日，顺义公安分局以廖某君等人涉嫌妨害传染病防治罪立案。
On March 6, Shunyi Public Security Bureau opened a case against Liao and others for allegedly obstructing the prevention and control of infectious diseases.
目前至少已有 18 例意大利输入型病例，主要从杭州、上海、北京入境。
There have been at least 18 imported cases from Italy, mainly from Hangzhou, Shanghai and Beijing.
。
