Wuhan prison, nursing home and other places confirmed 1795 cases of new crown pneumonia https: / / www.toutiao.com / i6801135198697161219 / March 7, 2007. As of March 5, 1,795 new cases and 164 suspected cases had been confirmed in Wuhan city prisons, public security detention centers, juvenile correctional institutions, nursing homes, mental hospitals and other special places.
”在 2 月 21 日首次公布数据是湖北监狱系统共感染 271 人，2月22日、23日，武汉养老院、福利院等场所被爆群聚感染。
The first data released on February 21 showed that 271 people had been infected with HIV / AIDS in the Hubei prison system.
