美国“至尊公主号”恐发生群聚感染，3500余人等待核酸检测http://international.caixin.com/2020-03-07/101525159.html据财新网报道，美国政府的新冠病毒工作小组负责人、副总统彭斯称，停靠加州的“至尊公主号”已测试 46 人，其中 21 人测试阳性（19人船员，2人乘客）。
More than 3,500 people are waiting for a nucleic acid test http: / / international.caixin.com / 2020-03-07 / 101525159.html, said Vice President Burns, who heads the U.S. government's New Crown Virus Task Force, and has tested 46 people, 21 of them positive (19 crew members and 2 passengers).
船上共有来自 54 个国家的 3533 人（2422 名乘客和1111 名船员），皆在船上等待核酸检测。
A total of 3,533 people (2,422 passengers and 1,111 crew members) from 54 countries were on board the ship awaiting nucleic acid testing.
但彭斯在 3 月 5 日称，新冠病毒检测试剂盒太少，无法满足需求。
But Burns said on March 5 that the new crown virus test kit was too few to meet demand.
。
.
“至尊公主”号与“钻石公主”号同属总部位于美国的「公主邮轮公司」旗下的同级邮轮，主要在加州、夏威夷、阿拉斯加和墨西哥之间航行。
The two ships are part of the U.S.-based Princess Cruises, which operates between California, Hawaii, Alaska and Mexico.
在“至尊公主”号上一趟行程（2月11日——2月21日）中，已有 7 名美国人和 2 名加拿大人确认感染，包括一名 3 月 4 日去世的 71 岁加州老人，而上一趟行程的约 2500 名乘客并没有在当时接受检测而直接下船，其中有 62 人继续参加了“至尊公主号”目前的旅程。
Seven Americans and two Canadians confirmed the infection, including a 71-year-old Californian who died on March 4, while about 2,500 of the last trip's 2,500 passengers did not disembark at the time, with 62 of them continuing on the current trip.
这趟行程在 2 月 21 日从旧金山出发，2 月 26 日抵达夏威夷并停靠多个岛屿，原定于 3 月 5 日抵达墨西哥，7 日返回旧金山，因 4 日得知去世的加州老人在上一次至尊公主”号的行程中，邮轮于 5 日直接返回旧金山，等待检测。
The trip began on February 21 in San Francisco, arrived in Hawaii on February 26 and docked on several islands. It was due to arrive in Mexico on March 5 and return to San Francisco on March 7.
美国政府对于乘客在船上接受隔离还是下船接受隔离没有决定，正在紧急联系上一批乘客。
The U. S. government has no decision on whether passengers will be quarantined or disembarked, and is urgently contacting a group of passengers.
。
.
截止美东时间 3 月 6 日晚间 7 时(北京 7 日上午 7 时)，全美共 25 个州出现新冠肺炎确诊病例 324 例，死亡病例 14 例，治愈病例 10 例。
By 7 p.m. March 6 (7: 00 a.m. Beijing 7), a total of 324 cases, 14 deaths and 10 cases of curable pneumonia had been diagnosed in 25 states across the United States.
其中西部的华盛顿州 80 例，加利福尼亚州 62 例，纽约州 44 例。
Of these, 80 were in the western state of Washington, 62 in California and 44 in New York.
。
