伊朗、意大利等国单日确诊破记录，世卫组织称全球确诊过10万https://news.sina.com.cn/w/2020-03-06/doc-iimxyqvz8445707.shtml据伊朗卫生部公布，3 月 6 日新增 1234 例，是伊朗单日新增最多的一天。
Countries such as Iran and Italy reported record-breaking one-day diagnoses, with the WHO saying 100,000 new cases were diagnosed globally at https: / / news.sina.com.cn / w / 2020-03-06 / doc-iimxyqvz845707.shtml, according to the Iranian Health Ministry.
目前累积 4747 例，死亡 124 例，其中国会议员感染率近 8%。
A cumulative total of 4,747 cases and 124 deaths have been recorded, with an infection rate of nearly 8 per cent among parliamentarians.
疫情已蔓延几乎所有省份。
The epidemic has spread to almost all provinces.
伊朗目前的试剂盒数量仍然无法满足检测需求，导致仍无法检测到真正的确诊人数。
The current number of test kits in Iran still falls short of testing needs, making it impossible to detect the true number of confirmed cases.
。
