据意大利政府公布，截止 3 月 6 日 18 时，当日新增 778 例，高出前一日 769 例，目前累计确诊 4636 例，死亡 197 例。
As of 18.00 on March 6, 778 new cases had been recorded, 769 more than the previous day, and 4,636 cases and 197 deaths had been confirmed, the Italian government said.
意大利的死亡人数超过伊朗。
The death toll in Italy exceeds that of Iran.
疫情主要集中在意大利北部，其中伦巴第大区发生医院感染，有超过 200 名医护人员感染。
The epidemic is concentrated mainly in northern Italy, where hospital infections occur in the Lombardy region, where more than 200 health-care workers are infected.
意大利麻醉医生和重症医生联合协会主席 Alessandro Vergallo 在本周称：“以目前的程度，我们不可能再坚持超过一周。
Alessandro Vergallo, president of the Italian Association of Anaesthesiologists and Physicians for Serious Disease, said this week: "At the current level, we can't last more than a week.
”世卫组织在 7 日的例行会议上称，全球确诊新冠肺炎患者已过 10 万。
More than 100,000 people have been diagnosed with pneumonia worldwide, the WHO said at a regular meeting yesterday.
。
