但根据官方数字，俄罗斯全国只有 10 例确诊病例（莫斯科 5 例）。
According to official figures, however, there were only 10 confirmed cases nationwide (5 in Moscow).
《纽约时报》称莫斯科实施严格的管制引发了更多猜测和疑虑。
The New York Times says Moscow's strict controls have led to more speculation and suspicion.
