More than half of the 37 Li Wenliang trademarks were registered by the Ali department of knowledge and production electrician http: / / china.caixin.com / 2020-03-07 / 101525137.html after rejecting 63 applications for registration of trademarks related to the outbreak of new crown pneumonia, citing adverse social impact, the trademark authorities again rejected 37 applications for registration of relevant trademarks of Li Wenliang.
