武汉小区居民在副总理视察期喊“假的”http://china.caixin.com/2020-03-06/101524711.html3 月 5 日上午 10 时，中央政治局委员、国务院副总理孙春兰与中央指导组等人，到武汉青山区开元公馆小区视察时，居民在小区开窗高喊“假的！假的！”“全部都是假的！”从现场视频可听出不止一户。
Wuhan residents during the Deputy Prime Minister's inspection period shouted "fake" http: / / china.caixin.com / 2020-03-06 / 101524711.htmlOn March 5, when Politburo member, Vice Premier Sun Chunlan and the Central Steering Group visited the district of Kaiyuan Mansion in Qingshan District of Wuhan.
据财新网等报道，社区存在着确诊病例通报不及时、社区封闭管理晚、楼内公共电梯消杀次数少的现象。
According to Caixin et al., there is a phenomenon of untimely notification of confirmed cases, late management of community closure and low number of public lifts in buildings.
“物业疫情期间不重视消毒，中央领导来了却大做特做，平时送菜不到位，这时候又赶紧摆样子。
"Property epidemic period does not attach importance to disinfection, the central leadership has come to do special, usually do not deliver dishes at this time quickly put on a show.
”一些“因为 2019 年车位费涨价维权”的业主被踢出微信群而无法拿到10元爱心蔬菜。
Some homeowners who are "defending themselves against 2019 parking fees" have been kicked out of the microcosm and are unable to get 10 yuan in love vegetables.
「中央指导组」在下午的「国新办」回应已开会要求“杜绝形式主义”。
