李文亮和王广发同时被表彰“先进个人”http://www.nhc.gov.cn/renshi/s7771/202003/28cc60d7e33b4dc7bd77af485fab1a58.shtml3 月 5 日，国家卫健委发布《关于表彰全国卫生健康系统新冠肺炎疫情防控工作先进集体和先进个人的决定》，「先进个人」的名单共表彰 506 人，其中有 34 位已去世。
Li Wenliang and Wang Guangfa were also praised as "advanced individuals" http: / / www.nhc.gov.cn / renshi / s7771 / 202003 / 28cc60d7e33b4d7bd77af485fa5a58.shtml.
名单上湖北省包括刘智明、李文亮、柳帆等 19 位医护人员因疫情而死亡，而河南、内蒙等地的有 3 位乡村医生死亡。
On the list, 19 medical workers in Hubei province, including Liu Zhiming, Li Wenliang and Liu Fan, died from the epidemic, while three rural doctors died in Henan, Inner Mongolia and other places.
在 1 月提出“人不传人”“可防可控”的王广发在「先进个人」名单的首页，并在名单出台后点赞了“不应该道歉”的微博。
Wang, who put forward the phrase "no human communication" and "defensible control" in January, wrote on the front page of the "Advanced Person" list and then posted a "No Apology" micro-blog.
